REM Title: Banner hello
REM Author: Cypher
REM Description: Prints a big banner via `banner` (BSD) or falls back to `say`.
REM Target: macOS
DELAY 500
GUI SPACE
DELAY 500
STRING Terminal
DELAY 1000
ENTER
DELAY 800
STRING banner -w 80 "HACKED" 2>/dev/null || say "you have been visited by the cypherbox"
ENTER
